authors.name: J.K. Rowling
authors.bio: British author, best known for her children's book series, J.K. Rowling's books include the main story arc series, the Harry Potter series, the Fantastic Beasts series, the Silvery Weasel series, the Goblet of Fire series, the Order of the Phoenix series, the Half-Blood Prince series, the Deathly Hallows series, and the Chamber of Secrets series.
